    <item>
      <title>NPC &amp; Boat Commands</title>
      <link>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/misc/npcboatcommands/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://zuluhotelomega.com/infovault/misc/npcboatcommands/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;merchants&#34;&gt;Merchants&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Dragging a stable pet deed onto an animal trainer will give the pet back to you.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;table-responsive&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;table class=&#34;table table-bordered table-hover table-striped&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;thead&#xA;        &gt;&#xA;          &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Command&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Information&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;    &lt;tbody&#xA;      &gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Sell bag&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will sell all the content of a targeted bag.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Sell all&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will sell all the items on you that is of the same kind of the targeted item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Sell&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will bring up a sell gump that allows you to select what items you want to sell.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Buy&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will bring up a buy menu that allows you to buy the selected items.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;vendor train/merchant train&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will bring up a skill training gump that allows you to train the selected skills to 33.3. Different vendors can train different skills.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;identify&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This command only works on mages or scribes and allows you to identify items or full bags with items.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;stable&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This command only works on animal trainers and will stable the selected pet.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;bankers&#34;&gt;Bankers&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-danger clearfix&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;float-start&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill hi-svg-inline alert-icon me-2&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; height=&#34;1em&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; width=&#34;1em&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5m.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2&#34;/&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;alert-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;First time opening your bank for that character? Close the bank box and open it again to make sure your items won’t bug away, no items can be replaced by staff if this happens.&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;table-responsive&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;table class=&#34;table table-bordered table-hover table-striped&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;thead&#xA;        &gt;&#xA;          &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Command&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Information&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;    &lt;tbody&#xA;      &gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;bank&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Will open your bank box.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;balance&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Shows the amount of gold you have in your bank.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;high-priests&#34;&gt;High Priests&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you hand over less gold then asked for you will make the priest upset at you and you will have to donate gold to him before you can use his services again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
